{
  "title": "Egyptian Chicken Drumsticks Stew",
  "description": "A tangy and creamy Egyptian dish featuring chicken drumsticks, this stew is a comforting and satvik-friendly meal option. It combines the richness of coconut milk with the brightness of lemon juice.",
