      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent and starting to caramelize.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken drumsticks and cook until they are browned on all sides.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and lemon juice, and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, until the chicken is cooked through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
